    <SectionLeft>
        <h2>Images</h2>
        <p>Images play nicely with cards. Simply include one outside of the <Code Content="PENhcmRTZWN0aW9uPg=="></Code> element to span nicely to the edges. Or move the image inside the <Code Content="PENhcmRTZWN0aW9uPg=="></Code> to have padding around the image.</p>
